  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nit would be less surprising for a user if anvil used the evm which was in place at the fork block height when forking, instead of the latest one. this requires adding a mapping of known chain ids to block heights to evm version running since that height.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nyou can see a similar feature implemented in ape-foundry here\r\nhttps://github.com/ApeWorX/ape-foundry/pull/9",
